column2: #generate a model of likelihood to bid for the fractal dependent on it's position,

glm(formula = fractal_bid ~ bundle_position + bundle_water_perc + 
    offer_value + trial, family = "binomial", data = task_data)
Null deviance: 68.841  on 119  degrees of freedom
Residual deviance: 45.690  on 115  degrees of freedom
